  "title": "Coordination Gap Under Damage Asymmetry",
  "concept": "When harm from a disruption spreads unevenly and the group absorbing the steepest collective damage cannot coordinate a unified response, decision power remains with parties facing lower individual costs who can negotiate while dispersed victims wait.",
  "interactiveId": "44080803-d1c3-4948-b40f-fdd51fdc0779",
  "sourcePieceId": "f59b30d5-0acb-43b9-a9c3-f118e6e67478",
  "publishedAt": 1778940657518,
  "voiceScore": 88,
  "qualityFlag": "low",
  "content": {
    "type": "html",
    "html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\">\n<title>Coordination Gap Under Damage Asymmetry</title>\n<style>\n  :root {\n    --bg: #faf7f1;\n    --fg: #1a1a1a;\n    --muted: #6b6b6b;\n    --line: #e5e0d6;\n    --gold: #c9a227;\n    --teal: #1a6b62;\n    --red: #c93a3a;\n  }\n  * { box-sizing: border-box; }\n  body {\n    font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, \"Segoe UI\", sans-serif;\n    margin: 0;\n    padding: 20px;\n    color: var(--fg);\n    background: var(--bg);\n    line-height: 1.5;\n  }\n  h2 {\n    font-size: 1.05rem;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    margin: 0 0 4px;\n  }\n  p.subhead {\n    margin: 0 0 20px;\n    color: var(--muted);\n    font-size: 0.9rem;\n  }\n  .control {\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    gap: 14px;\n    margin-bottom: 20px;\n  }\n  .control label {\n    font-weight: 500;\n    flex-shrink: 0;\n  }\n  .control input[type=range] {\n    flex: 1;\n    accent-color: var(--teal);\n    min-width: 120px;\n  }\n  .control output {\n    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    min-width: 2ch;\n    text-align: right;\n  }\n  .actors {\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;\n    gap: 20px;\n    margin: 24px 0;\n  }\n  .actor-box {\n    padding: 16px;\n    background: #fff;\n    border: 2px solid var(--line);\n    border-radius: 8px;\n  }\n  .actor-label {\n    font-size: 0.75rem;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    letter-spacing: 0.06em;\n    color: var(--muted);\n    margin-bottom: 8px;\n  }\n  .damage-bar {\n    height: 100px;\n    background: var(--line);\n    border-radius: 4px;\n    position: relative;\n    overflow: hidden;\n    margin-bottom: 12px;\n  }\n  .damage-fill {\n    position: absolute;\n    bottom: 0;\n    left: 0;\n    right: 0;\n    background: var(--red);\n    transition: height 200ms ease-out;\n  }\n  .metrics {\n    font-size: 0.85rem;\n    display: flex;\n    flex-direction: column;\n    gap: 4px;\n  }\n  .metric-row {\n    display: flex;\n    justify-content: space-between;\n  }\n  .metric-label {\n    color: var(--muted);\n  }\n  .metric-value {\n    font-weight: 600;\n    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;\n  }\n  .dispersed-box {\n    grid-column: 1 / -1;\n    background: #fff9f0;\n    border-color: var(--gold);\n  }\n  .coordination-demo {\n    margin-top: 12px;\n    padding: 12px;\n    background: var(--bg);\n    border-radius: 4px;\n  }\n  .coord-label {\n    font-size: 0.8rem;\n    color: var(--muted);\n    margin-bottom: 8px;\n  }\n  .coord-button {\n    width: 100%;\n    padding: 10px;\n    font-size: 0.9rem;\n    font-weight: 500;\n    border: 2px solid var(--line);\n    border-radius: 4px;\n    background: var(--line);\n    color: var(--muted);\n    cursor: not-allowed;\n    position: relative;\n  }\n  .coord-button::after {\n    content: '';\n    position: absolute;\n    inset: 0;\n    background: repeating-linear-gradient(\n      45deg,\n      transparent,\n      transparent 8px,\n      rgba(0,0,0,0.05) 8px,\n      rgba(0,0,0,0.05) 16px\n    );\n    pointer-events: none;\n  }\n  .reading {\n    margin: 18px 0 6px;\n    padding: 12px 16px;\n    background: #fff;\n    border: 1px solid var(--line);\n    border-radius: 6px;\n    font-size: 0.9rem;\n  }\n  .reading strong {\n    font-weight: 600;\n  }\n  p.caption {\n    margin: 14px 0 0;\n    color: var(--muted);\n    font-size: 0.875rem;\n  }\n  @media (max-width: 600px) {\n    .actors {\n      grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n    }\n    .dispersed-box {\n      grid-column: 1;\n    }\n    .damage-bar {\n      height: 80px;\n    }\n  }\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n<h2>Drag to extend the disruption</h2>\n<p class=\"subhead\">A resource stops flowing. Damage spreads unevenly. One group can coordinate a response; the other cannot.</p>\n\n<div class=\"control\">\n  <label for=\"days\">Days:</label>\n  <input id=\"days\" type=\"range\" min=\"0\" max=\"12\" value=\"0\" step=\"1\" aria-describedby=\"days-out\">\n  <output id=\"days-out\" for=\"days\">0</output>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"actors\">\n  <div class=\"actor-box\">\n    <div class=\"actor-label\">Decision-maker A</div>\n    <div class=\"damage-bar\">\n      <div class=\"damage-fill\" id=\"damage-a\"></div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"metrics\">\n      <div class=\"metric-row\">\n        <span class=\"metric-label\">Per day:</span>\n        <span class=\"metric-value\" id=\"cost-a\">0</span>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"metric-row\">\n        <span class=\"metric-label\">Total:</span>\n        <span class=\"metric-value\" id=\"total-a\">0</span>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"metric-row\">\n        <span class=\"metric-label\">Can negotiate:</span>\n        <span class=\"metric-value\">Yes</span>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"actor-box\">\n    <div class=\"actor-label\">Decision-maker B</div>\n    <div class=\"damage-bar\">\n      <div class=\"damage-fill\" id=\"damage-b\"></div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"metrics\">\n      <div class=\"metric-row\">\n        <span class=\"metric-label\">Per day:</span>\n        <span class=\"metric-value\" id=\"cost-b\">0</span>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"metric-row\">\n        <span class=\"metric-label\">Total:</span>\n        <span class=\"metric-value\" id=\"total-b\">0</span>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"metric-row\">\n        <span class=\"metric-label\">Can negotiate:</span>\n        <span class=\"metric-value\">Yes</span>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"actor-box dispersed-box\">\n    <div class=\"actor-label\">Dispersed group (many individuals)</div>\n    <div class=\"damage-bar\">\n      <div class=\"damage-fill\" id=\"damage-dispersed\"></div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"metrics\">\n      <div class=\"metric-row\">\n        <span class=\"metric-label\">Per day (total):</span>\n        <span class=\"metric-value\" id=\"cost-dispersed\">0</span>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"metric-row\">\n        <span class=\"metric-label\">Total:</span>\n        <span class=\"metric-value\" id=\"total-dispersed\">0</span>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"metric-row\">\n        <span class=\"metric-label\">Can negotiate:</span>\n        <span class=\"metric-value\">No</span>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"coordination-demo\">\n      <div class=\"coord-label\">Coordination mechanism:</div>\n      <button class=\"coord-button\" disabled>Force resolution (disabled — no unified voice)</button>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"reading\">\n  Highest total damage: <strong id=\"damage-leader\">none yet</strong>.\n  <span id=\"damage-detail\"></span>\n</div>\n\n<p class=\"caption\" id=\"caption\">Move the slider. The group with the steepest collective cost has no mechanism to compel a settlement.</p>\n\n<script>\n(function() {\n  var slider = document.getElementById('days');\n  var daysOut = document.getElementById('days-out');\n  var damageA = document.getElementById('damage-a');\n  var damageB = document.getElementById('damage-b');\n  var damageDispersed = document.getElementById('damage-dispersed');\n  var costA = document.getElementById('cost-a');\n  var costB = document.getElementById('cost-b');\n  var costDispersed = document.getElementById('cost-dispersed');\n  var totalA = document.getElementById('total-a');\n  var totalB = document.getElementById('total-b');\n  var totalDispersed = document.getElementById('total-dispersed');\n  var damageLeader = document.getElementById('damage-leader');\n  var damageDetail = document.getElementById('damage-detail');\n  var caption = document.getElementById('caption');\n\n  function fmt(n) {\n    return Math.round(n).toLocaleString();\n  }\n\n  function update() {\n    var days = +slider.value;\n    daysOut.textContent = days;\n\n    // A: moderate per-day cost, can negotiate\n    var perA = 120;\n    var runningA = days * perA;\n    costA.textContent = fmt(perA);\n    totalA.textContent = fmt(runningA);\n    var pctA = Math.min(100, (runningA / 1200) * 100);\n    damageA.style.height = pctA + '%';\n\n    // B: low per-day cost, can negotiate\n    var perB = 60;\n    var runningB = days * perB;\n    costB.textContent = fmt(perB);\n    totalB.textContent = fmt(runningB);\n    var pctB = Math.min(100, (runningB / 1200) * 100);\n    damageB.style.height = pctB + '%';\n\n    // Dispersed: high collective cost, cannot coordinate\n    var perDispersed = 450;\n    var runningDispersed = days * perDispersed;\n    costDispersed.textContent = fmt(perDispersed);\n    totalDispersed.textContent = fmt(runningDispersed);\n    var pctDispersed = Math.min(100, (runningDispersed / 1200) * 100);\n    damageDispersed.style.height = pctDispersed + '%';\n\n    if (days === 0) {\n      damageLeader.textContent = 'none yet';\n      damageDetail.textContent = '';\n      caption.textContent = 'Move the slider. The group with the steepest collective cost has no mechanism to compel a settlement.';\n    } else if (days <= 2) {\n      damageLeader.textContent = 'dispersed group';\n      damageDetail.textContent = 'Spread across many individuals, the total harm outpaces either decision-maker. But there is no unified voice to force action.';\n      caption.textContent = 'Collective damage exceeds individual damage, but coordination failure keeps the dispersed group from responding.';\n    } else if (days <= 5) {\n      damageLeader.textContent = 'dispersed group, by far';\n      damageDetail.textContent = 'The gap widens. Decision-makers A and B together absorb less damage than the group that has no seat at the negotiation.';\n      caption.textContent = 'The asymmetry grows. The party bearing the steepest cost remains structurally excluded from stopping the disruption.';\n    } else {\n      damageLeader.textContent = 'dispersed group, severely';\n      damageDetail.textContent = 'Frustration mounts, but without a single point of leverage the dispersed group cannot intervene. A and B still control timing.';\n      caption.textContent = 'Time deepens the imbalance. The group with the highest total damage still has no path to force resolution.';\n    }\n  }\n\n  slider.addEventListener('input', update);\n  update();\n})();\n</script>\n</body>\n</html>"
  }
}
